  <li>дё»зӘ—еҸЈ: <code class="highlighter-rouge">window</code>пјҢеҸҠдё»зӘ—еҸЈзҡ„дёҖдәӣеҹәжң¬еұһжҖ§пјҲж ҮйўҳгҖҒеӨ§е°Ҹпјү</li>
  <li>и®©зӘ—еҸЈжҙ»иө·жқҘпјҡ<code class="highlighter-rouge">window.mainloop()</code></li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">tkinter</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">tk</span>

