</span><span class="n">windo</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">mainloop</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="зӘ—еҸЈеҶ…е®№пјҲзӘ—еҸЈдёҠзҡ„жҺ§д»¶пјү">зӘ—еҸЈеҶ…е®№пјҲзӘ—еҸЈдёҠзҡ„жҺ§д»¶пјү
  <a href="/tutorials/python-basic/tkinter/2-02-entry-text/#зӘ—еҸЈеҶ…е®№пјҲзӘ—еҸЈдёҠзҡ„жҺ§д»¶пјү" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>еҲӣе»әжҢүй’®еҲҶеҲ«и§ҰеҸ‘дёӨз§Қжғ…еҶө</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">b1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">window</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"insert point"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">width</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">15</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">height</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">command</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">insert_point</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">b1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="n">b2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Button</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">window</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"insert end"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">command</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">insert_end</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">b2</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>еҲӣе»әиҫ“е…ҘжЎҶentryпјҢз”ЁжҲ·иҫ“е…Ҙд»»дҪ•еҶ…е®№йғҪжҳҫзӨәдёә*</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">e</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Entry</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">window</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">show</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">'*'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">e</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>еҲӣе»әдёҖдёӘж–Үжң¬жЎҶз”ЁдәҺжҳҫзӨә</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">t</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tk</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Text</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">window</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">height</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pack</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>е®ҡд№үи§ҰеҸ‘дәӢд»¶ж—¶зҡ„еҮҪж•°пјҲжіЁж„Ҹпјҡеӣ дёәPythonзҡ„жү§иЎҢйЎәеәҸжҳҜд»ҺдёҠеҫҖдёӢпјҢжүҖд»ҘеҮҪж•°дёҖе®ҡиҰҒж”ҫеңЁжҢүй’®зҡ„дёҠйқўпјү</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">insert_point</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">var</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">insert</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'insert'</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">var</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">insert_end</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">var</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">t</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">insert</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'end'</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">var</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

